federation</div></div></div><p class=\"mt-4 text-sm text-gray-300 leading-relaxed\">巴西是足球史上最成功的國家，五度奪得世界盃冠軍。以華麗的森巴足球風格聞名全球，每屆世界盃都是奪冠熱門。</p></div></div><section class=\"mb-8\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4\">小組積分</h2><div class=\"grid gap-6 \"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"px-4 py-3\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg, #2d47cb 0%, #2339a8 100%)\"><h3 class=\"text-white font-bold text-lg\">Group C</h3></div><div class=\"overflow-x-auto\"><table class=\"w-full text-sm\"><thead><tr class=\"border-b border-gray-100 bg-gray-50\"><th class=\"px-3 py-2 text-left text-gray-500 font-medium w-8\">#</th><th class=\"px-3 py-2 text-left text-gray-500 font-medium\">隊伍</th><th class=\"px-3 py-2 text-center text-gray-500 font-medium\">賽</th><th class=\"px-3 py-2 text-center text-gray-500 font-medium\">勝</th><th class=\"px-3 py-2 text-center text-gray-500 font-medium\">和</th><th class=\"px-3 py-2 text-center text-gray-500 font-medium\">敗</th><th class=\"px-3 py-2 text-center text-gray-500 font-medium\">進</th><th class=\"px-3 py-2 text-center text-gray-500 font-medium\">失</th><th class=\"px-3 py-2 text-center text-gray-500 font-medium\">差</th><th class=\"px-3 py-2 text-center text-gray-500 font-medium font-bold\">分</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class=\"border-b border-gray-50 hover:bg-blue-50/50 transition-colors bg-green-50/30\"><td class=\"px-3 py-2.5 text-center\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-green-100 text-green-700 text-xs font-bold\">1</span></td><td class=\"px-3 py-2.5\"><a href=\"/teams/brazil\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\"><span class=\"fi fi-br fis text-base rounded-sm\" title=\"Brazil\"></span><span class=\"text-sm font-medium text-gray-800\">巴西</span></div></a></td><td class=\"px-3 py-2.5 text-center text-gray-700\">0</td><td class=\"px-3 py-2.5 text-center text-gray-700\">0</td><td class=\"px-3 py-2.5 text-center text-gra